metadata.name: The God of Filters
metadata.description:
The God of Filters collects, selects and shows all the information meant to you. Living in the realms of the multiverse dimensions, he defines your reality. It never stops; always enjoying the reactions, playing with the realities.
In this hyper informative world, where do you get the information about your reality? What information do you consume? What reality do you build or is build in front of you?
